## Agent Names

The following agent names are configured for this project. Always use
the name shown for each role as the `subagent_type` parameter when
spawning agents via the Agent/Task tool.

- **reviewer agent**: my-reviewer
- **browser analyser agent**: accelerator:browser-analyser
- **browser locator agent**: accelerator:browser-locator
- **codebase locator agent**: my-locator
- **codebase analyser agent**: accelerator:codebase-analyser
- **codebase pattern finder agent**: accelerator:codebase-pattern-finder
- **documents locator agent**: accelerator:documents-locator
- **documents analyser agent**: accelerator:documents-analyser
- **web search researcher agent**: accelerator:web-search-researcher
